OL,3,CPolice given more time to question
OL,4,Cmurder suspects
OL,6,FDetectives have been given extra time
OL,7,Fto question three men arrested as part
OL,8,Fof a murder investigation into the
OL,9,Fdeath of an 18-year-old.
OL,11,FDorset Police received a report at
OL,12,F2.13am on Friday that a man had been
OL,13,Ffound with injuries in Longfleet Road
OL,14,Fin Poole,
OL,16,FThe male victim, who was from Poole,
OL,17,Fwas taken to hospital for treatment
OL,18,Ffor a suspected stab wound and
OL,19,Fpronounced dead shortly after.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
