OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782147993
OL,3,CPolice given more time to question
OL,4,Cmurder suspects
OL,6,FPolice said they believe he sustained
OL,7,Finjuries during an incident in Dale
OL,8,FClose and was then taken to Longfleet
OL,9,FRoad in a car.
OL,11,FOn Sunday, Dorset Police said they had
OL,12,Fbeen granted additional time by a
OL,13,Fcourt to question two 22-year-olds,
OL,14,Fone from Bletchley in Buckinghamshire
OL,15,Fand one from London, and a 20-year-old
OL,16,Fman from Blandford who had all been
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
