OL,3,CPolice given more time to question
OL,4,Cmurder suspects
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Neil Third,
OL,7,Fof Dorset Police, said: "We are
OL,8,Fkeeping the victim's family updated on
OL,9,Four progress and our thoughts are with
OL,10,Fthem at this incredibly difficult time.
OL,12,F"Our investigation is progressing at
OL,13,Fpace and we believe a Nissan Juke was
OL,14,Finvolved in the incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782147993
OL,3,CPolice given more time to question
OL,4,Cmurder suspects
OL,6,F"We are keen to piece together its
OL,7,Fmovements during the night and are
OL,8,Fasking members of the public who may
OL,9,Fhave been travelling between Dale Road
OL,10,Fand Blandford or those living along
OL,11,Fthe route to review any dashcam
OL,12,Ffootage or home CCTV for any sightings
OL,13,Fof a vehicle matching the description.
OL,15,F"Officers are also continuing to
OL,16,Fsearch a property in Castleman Smith
OL,17,FClose in Blandford in connection to
OL,18,Fthe incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782147993
OL,3,CPolice given more time to question
OL,4,Cmurder suspects
OL,6,F"We do not underestimate the concern
OL,7,Fand upset that an incident of this
OL,8,Fnature will have in the community and
OL,9,Fofficers from the neighbourhood
OL,10,Fpolicing team are carrying out
OL,11,Fadditional patrols in the area and can
OL,12,Fbe approached with any questions or
OL,13,Fconcerns.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
