OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782147993
OL,3,CPolice given more time to question
OL,4,Cmurder suspects
OL,6,F"We still need help from the public
OL,7,Fand would reiterate our appeal for
OL,8,Fanyone with information - or relevant
OL,9,Fhome CCTV, doorbell camera or dashcam
OL,10,Ffootage - from Dale Close, Longfleet
OL,11,FRoad and the route to Blandford around
OL,12,Fthe relevant time to please contact
OL,13,Fus."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
